Class DropListenerCollection

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable, java.util.Collection, java.util.List, java.util.RandomAccess
public class DropListenerCollection
extends java.util.Vector

The central collection of all drop objects and events. Affects the drop listeners and contains all fired methods which allow to add a drop listener to the widgets.

add

public void add(DropListener listener,
                com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget w)
Adds a DropListenerCollection to unique Vector List from MouseDragGestureRecognizer. This list will be analyzed so that a dragging widget could find a dropping target.

Parameters:
listener - the event to be listened.
w - the widget associated to a drop target.
